ğŸ“‚ Level 1 â†’ Level 2
ğŸ¯ Goal

Find the password stored in a file named readme in the home directory.

ğŸ” Approach

After logging in, I used basic Linux commands:

ls
cat readme

The password was directly inside the readme file.

ğŸ§  What I Learned

